{"tid":1471359,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"這一「撚」如此精確形容三類今次運動上見到嘅人","createTime":"2019-08-14T08:59:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T08:59:17.000Z","uid":306223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a83cdfed5f0a3b16f536600fb8ddb438afecf0d9","tid":1471359,"uid":306223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T08:59:17.000Z","msg":"<strong>1. 撚酸</strong><br />\n<br />\n(粵音：nan2 syun1; 國語拼音：niǎn suān) 活得非但卑微如塵土，而且扭曲如蛆蟲的人，當看到有別人嘗試伸直腰板，嘗試我口講我心，但自己卻沒有這份勇氣，當然是會妒恨的。不過他們不但任由自己由裏到外發出酸腐氣味，還手口並用地在地鐵、在酒樓、在長輩whatapp群組中將之到處散播，卻真是影響市容了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OaJSgjE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOaJSgjE.jpg&h=31f5c80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 紙撚</strong><br />\n<br />\n他們只知到處找碴生事、煽風點火，就像用作引火的紙繩一樣<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 撚靶</strong><br />\n<br />\n也有些專門靠為權貴做猴子戲為生的政治臨記，低至在法庭門外侮辱法官種族的嘍囉，高至有特別英語技巧的留洋立法會議員，還有臨場連台詞科介都忘記了的政壇裙腳仔，這些人就像挑擔賣雜貨的貨郎，必須轉動手中小鼓，不斷發出單調空洞的聲音吸引顧客一樣。而這種人嘛，在元代戲曲之中也有個專屬的名稱，叫作「撚靶(兒)」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人認為 何撚靶 一名不失霸氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文: <a href=\"https://medium.com/@leungtokhoi/%E6%92%9A-%E6%B2%92%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E6%9C%83%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E9%80%99%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E7%B2%97%E5%8F%A3-776ade9640c6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40leungtokhoi%2F%25E6%2592%259A-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2589%258D%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%2582%25BA%25E9%2580%2599%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E7%25B2%2597%25E5%258F%25A3-776ade9640c6&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3d2UZYMvR53lMa2%2BnKJB5b4%3D&h=d46b710c\" target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@leungtokhoi/%E6%92%9A-%E6%B2%92%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E6%89%8D%E6%9C%83%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E9%80%99%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E7%B2%97%E5%8F%A3-776ade9640c6</a>"}]}